hadiths[11]{hadithnumber,text}:
2014,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs Ramazan ke rozey eman aur ehtisaab (ajr w sawab hasil karney ki niiyat) ke sath rakhey , iske pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. aur jo lailatul-qadr mein eman w ehtisaab ke sath Namaz mein khada rahe iske bhi pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, Sufiyan ke sath Sulaiman-bin Kasir ne bhi us hadis ko Zohri se riwayat kya."
2015,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand ashaab ko shabe-qadr khuwab mein (ramazaan ki) saat (7) aakhiri taareekhon mein dikhai gaee thi. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main dekh raha hun ke tumharey sab ke khuwab saat (7) aakhiri taareekhon par muttafiq ho gaey hain. isliye jisey uski talash ho wo usi hafta ki aakhiri ( taaq ( raaton mein talash kare.
2016,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ramazan ke doosrey Ashrey mein aetikaf mein baithey. phir bees taareekh ki subah ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf se nikley aur hamein khutba diya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey lailatul-Qadr dikhai gaee, lekin bhulaa di gaee ya (aap ne ye farmaya ke) mein khud bhool gaya. isliye tum usey aakhiri Ashrey ki taaq raaton mein talash karo. maine ye bhi dekha hai) khuwab mein) ke maano mein keechad mein sajda kar raha hun. isliye jisne mere sath aetikaf kya ho wo phir lot aaey aur aetikaf mein baithey. khair ham ne phir aetikaf kya. us waqt aasman par badalon ka aik tukda bhi nahi tha. lekin dekhtey hi dekhtey badal aaya aur barish itni hui ke masjid ki chhat se pani tapakney laga jo khajoor ki shakhon se bani hui thi. phir Namaz ki takbeer hui to maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) keechad mein sajda kar rahe they. yahan tak ke keechad ka nishan maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peshani par dekha."
2017,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, shabe-qadr ko Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey ki taaq raaton mein dhoondo ."
2018,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke us Ashrey mein aetikaf kya kartey jo mahiney ke beej mein padta hai. bees raaton ke guzar janey ke baad jab ikkeeswiin taareekh ki raat aati to Sham ko aap ghar wapas aa jatey. jo log aap ke sath aetikaf mein hotey wo bhi apne gharon mein wapas aa jatey. aik Ramazan mein aap jab aetikaf kiye huey they, to us raat mein bhi (masjid hi mein) muqeem rahe jis mein aap ki aadat ghar aa janey ki thi, phir aap ne logon ko khutba diya aur jo kuchh Allah paak ne chaha , aap ne logon ko iska hukm diya, phir farmaya ke main us (doosrey ( Ashrey mein aetikaf kya karta tha, lekin ab mujh par ye zahir na hua ke ab us aakhiri Ashrey mein mujhey aetikaf karna chahiye isliye jisne mere sath aetikaf kya hai wo apne eitikaaf ki jagah hi mein thehra rahe aur mujhey ye raat ( shabe-qadr ( dikhai gaee lekin phir bhulwaa di gaee. isliye tum log usey aakhiri Ashrey (ki taaq raaton ( mein talash karo. maine ( khuwab mein) apne ko dekha ke us raat keechad mein sajda kar raha hun. phir us raat aasman par abr hua aur barish barsii, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Namaz padhney ki jagah (chhat se) pani tapakney laga. ye ikkeeswiin ki raat ka zikr hai. maine khud apni aankhon se dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz ke baad wapas ho rahe they. aur aap ke chehra Mubarak par keechad lagi hui thi."
2019,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (shabe-qadr ko) talash karo.
2020,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey mein aetikaf kartey aur farmatey ke Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey mein shabe-qadr ko talash karo.
2021,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, shabe-qadr ko Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey mein talash karo, jab nau (9) raatein baqi reh jayen ya saat (7) ya panch raatein baqi reh jaaein. (yani ikkeesviin ya teiswiin ya pachiswin raaton mein shabe-qadr ko talash karo) ."
2022,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya shabe-qadr Ramazan ke) aakhiri ( Ashrey mein padtii hai. jab nau (9) raatein guzar jayen ya saat (7) baqi reh jaaein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad shabe-qadr se thi. abdul-wahaab ne Ayub aur Khalid se bayan kya, unse Ikrima ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke shabe-qadr ko chobis taareekh (ki raat ( mein talash karo."
2023,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein shabe-qadr ki khabar dene ke liye tashrif la rahe they ke 2 musalman aapas mein jhagdaa karne lagey. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aaya tha ke tumhen shabe-qadr bata dun lekin falan-falan ne aapas mein jhagdaa kar liya. to iska ilm utha liya gaya aur ummeed yahi hai ke tumharey haq mein yahi behtar hoga. to ab tum uski talash (aakhirii Ashrey ki) nau (9) ya saat (7) ya panch (ki raaton ( mein kya karo.
2024,jab (ramazaan ka ( aakhiri Ashrey aata to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna tehband mazbut baandhtey (yani apni kamar poori tarah kas letey) aur un raaton mein aap khud bhi jaagtey aur apne ghar walon ko bhi jagaaya kartey they.
